{"tid":302293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[方丈猁]沙拿舊tweet激嬲利迷","createTime":"2017-06-29T09:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T12:17:14.000Z","uid":31598,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da48d5a636f77473767417d2b8775b34a984a620","tid":302293,"uid":31598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=lg%2B1TphMmDxEVufsZITl72i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9de30159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】身為公眾人物，大部份都逃不過被網民起底和秋後算賬的命運，利物浦新兵穆罕默德沙拿就是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah）剛以3900萬鎊從羅馬加盟利物浦，令一眾紅軍球迷歡天喜地，紛紛追蹤其社交網站，當其粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就發現沙拿去年7月曾於twitter，上載了一張自己和丹巴巴亞在車路士並肩作戰的相片，留言祝那時受重傷的前隊友早日康復。看到這張相片後，很多利迷都大表憤怒，更留言叫沙拿刪除這個post和相片。<br />\n<br />\n何解？原來這張相片拍自2014年4月27日車路士對利物浦的英超，利物浦在這場比賽因為謝拉特跣腳，被丹巴巴亞截得皮球後射入，最終落敗失卻英超冠軍。一眾紅軍球迷看到這相片，就回憶起這段慘痛歷史；未知在該仗正選上陣踢了60分鐘的沙拿，會不會「屈服」？<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=18404158280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D18404158280&d=lg%2B1TphMmDxEVufsZITl72i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f444b00c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=18404158280</a>"},{"pid":"c2d5b9ecefd559c75154b0ecb29d6729cf1a32fb","tid":302293,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932adc9c8124971f349677bf50194c01ef3c2e32","tid":302293,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c040b6aa259f3e16bfe33340c6f22d43504fe3","tid":302293,"uid":9652